commit.message: Add github action CI and remove Travis.
Bump version to 1.9.

Change the printf format specifier from long to double, and compute the
difftime of the time_t end_wall_time.tv_sec against 0; this avoids a
compilation error on x32 due to casting a time_t to long, when it's a
long long on that platform.  (I.e. this is a more portable way to do
it.)
Depend on 'all' for test, so the binaries are built!  Remove the shell debug trace.
Print regtest steps.
Add build status indicator to README.
Add travis.yml for continuous build.
Fix changelog for new version.
New upstream release.
